---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started | Boat & RV Guardian">
	<section class="page-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="eyebrow">Getting Started</span>
			<h1>Set up your Guardian system</h1>
			<p>Everything from mounting the valve at the spigot to wiring webhooks and understanding how the pieces talk to each other. New here? Looking for help instead of how-tos? Head to <a href="/support">Support</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="container main-content">

		<!-- Quick Start -->
		<section class="quickstart">
			<div class="step glass-card">
				<span class="step-num">1</span>
				<h3>Choose your hardware</h3>
				<p>Pick a kit or individual LinkTap and Shelly components on the <a href="/devices">Supported Devices</a> page — with estimated prices.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="step glass-card">
				<span class="step-num">2</span>
				<h3>Install the app</h3>
				<p>Launch the web dashboard or install a native app from the <a href="/#downloads">downloads</a> section, then sign in.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="step glass-card">
				<span class="step-num">3</span>
				<h3>Connect &amp; configure</h3>
				<p>Add your gateway, pair sensors, set flow limits, and wire up alerts using the guides below.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Physical Setup Guide -->
		<section class="doc-section">
			<div class="glass-card">
				<h2>Physical installation best practices</h2>
				<p>For a smart water valve, physical placement matters as much as the software. To maximize protection, install the valve directly at the <strong>source spigot</strong> — not inside your rig or on its city-water inlet.</p>

				<div class="setup-grid">
					<div>
						<h3>The ideal configuration</h3>
						<ol class="setup-steps">
							<li><strong>Source spigot</strong> — the campsite or marina water source</li>
							<li><strong>Smart water valve</strong> — LinkTap, attached directly to the spigot</li>
							<li><strong>Water hose</strong> — connects the valve to your rig</li>
							<li><strong>RV/Boat city-water inlet</strong></li>
						</ol>

						<h3>Why place the valve at the source?</h3>
						<p>Many owners mount regulators, filters, and valves on the inlet at the side of the RV. <strong>That leaves the hose itself completely unprotected.</strong></p>
						<p>Hoses face UV, wear, and pressure swings. If one bursts while you're away and the valve is downstream, it can't stop a leak happening <em>before</em> it. At the spigot, the valve guards the hose and everything after it.</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Benefits of source-spigot install</h3>
						<ul class="benefits-list">
							<li><strong>Complete hose protection:</strong> abnormal continuous flow trips the valve and shuts water off at the source.</li>
							<li><strong>Internal plumbing protection:</strong> still fully protects everything inside the rig.</li>
							<li><strong>Less strain on the inlet:</strong> heavy valves and gateways sit on the sturdy metal spigot, not your rig's plastic fittings.</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>Extra tips</h3>
						<ul class="benefits-list">
							<li><strong>Support heavy setups:</strong> with Y-splitters or add-ons, use a hose stand to take weight off the spigot.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Architecture Diagram -->
		<section class="doc-section">
			<div class="glass-card">
				<h2>How it all connects</h2>
				<div class="arch-flow">
					<div class="arch-lane">
						<span class="lane-label local">Local network — when you're aboard</span>
						<div class="lane-row">
							<span class="node">📱 Phone / Laptop</span>
							<span class="arrow">&harr;</span>
							<span class="node">📡 LinkTap Gateway</span>
							<span class="arrow">&harr;</span>
							<span class="node">💧 Smart Valve</span>
						</div>
						<p>Direct, zero-latency control with no internet required.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="arch-lane">
						<span class="lane-label cloud">Cloud alerts — when you're away</span>
						<div class="lane-row">
							<span class="node">🌊 Flood Sensor</span>
							<span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
							<span class="node">☁️ Cloudflare Worker</span>
							<span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
							<span class="node">🔔 Push Notification</span>
							<span class="arrow">+</span>
							<span class="node">💧 Remote Valve Shutoff</span>
						</div>
						<p>Sensors fire to the edge network, which alerts you and closes the valve via the LinkTap API.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.main-content { padding-bottom: 2rem; }

	/* Quick start */
	.quickstart {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.step { padding: 2rem; }

	.step-num {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--accent-gradient);
		color: #fff;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.step h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
	.step p { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }

	/* Doc sections */
	.doc-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

	.doc-section > .glass-card { padding: 2.5rem; }

	.doc-section h2 {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.doc-section > .glass-card > p { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }
	.doc-section strong { color: #fff; }

	.setup-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.setup-grid h3 {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--accent-color);
		margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.setup-grid h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

	.setup-steps, .benefits-list {
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-main);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.setup-steps li, .benefits-list li { margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }

	code {
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.note {
		background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.08);
		padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
		border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	/* Architecture flow */
	.arch-flow {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.arch-lane {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.4);
	}

	.lane-label {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
	}

	.lane-label.local { color: var(--success-color); background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.25); }
	.lane-label.cloud { color: var(--accent-hover); background: rgba(14,165,233,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.25); }

	.lane-row {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.node {
		background: var(--surface-color);
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.arrow { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1.2rem; }

	.arch-lane p { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }

	/* Guides grid */
	.section-h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

	.guides-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.guide-card {
		display: block;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		padding: 1.75rem;
	}

	.guide-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-color); }
	.guide-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
	.guide-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #fff; }
	.guide-card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
	.read-more { color: var(--accent-color); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.88rem; }

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.setup-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
		.doc-section > .glass-card { padding: 1.75rem; }
	}
</style>
